abstract: What's inside an iPhone 4S? The team over at ifixit, a popular free repair Web site, dissected the new phone to see Apple's latest chips and sensors.
snippet: What's inside an iPhone 4S? The team over at ifixit, a popular free repair Web site, dissected the new phone to see Apple's latest chips and sensors.
lead_paragraph: The team over at ifixit, a popular free repair manual Web site, has been busy dissecting Apple's iPhone 4S like a frog in a science classroom.
